DESCRIPTION:Description GSBA Open House Happy Hour Join us for an open-hous
	e style happy hour and spend some time connecting with the GSBA community.
	 This casual networking event is designed for new members and longtime mem
	bers alike who want to build relationships\, reconnect with GSBA\, and lea
	rn more about the people and programs behind our work. Enjoy light snacks\
	, drinks \\(including non-alcoholic options\\)\, and easy conversation whi
	le meeting fellow members and the GSBA team. Event Details Date: Monday\, 
	February 23 Time: 4:00-5:30 PM Notes: Snacks and drinks will be provided\,
	 with non-alcoholic options available. What to Expect A Welcoming Space to
	 Connect Spend time in an open\, relaxed setting designed to make it easy 
	to meet people and start conversations. Member-to-Member Networking Connec
	t with other GSBA members-especially those who are new or looking to deepe
	n their involvement. Meet the GSBA Team Our staff will be on hand to intro
	duce themselves\, answer questions\, and share how our programs support me
	mbers throughout the year. Member Benefits Overview Learn more about GSBA 
	benefits\, events\, and opportunities-and how to make the most of your mem
	bership. Open Conversation Bring your ideas\, questions\, and updates. Thi
	s is an informal space to connect\, listen\, and share.\n\nFrom SEAtoday -
	 Food & Drink
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/gsba-open-house/17865903/
	2026-02-23T00
